data.eml:eml: An enigmatic new genus of cyclostome braconid wasp (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) from New Zealand

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Belokobylskij, Sergey A. (2018): An enigmatic new genus of cyclostome braconid wasp (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) from New Zealand. Zootaxa 4403 (3): 594-600, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4403.3.12
